snippet.title: Feeding 1000 BOOM Plorts to a BLACK HOLE Slime - Slime Rancher Mod
snippet.description:
These slimes are best friends. In this mod, the Black Hole Slime and the While Hole Slime pair together to make the new Singularity Slime duo! This is a family friendly Slime Rancher gameplay video.

TUBBZ Info! : http://www.numskull.com/tubbz/

Mod credit to Veesus, available here: https://www.nexusmods.com/slimerancher/mods/21

MORE SLIME RANCHER VIDEOS: http://bit.ly/PartyGordoUpdate

Hope you enjoyed this Let's Play Slime Rancher video!

Don't forget to hit like and share the video!
